{"tid":1450863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:03:41.000Z","uid":4335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a85dd592ff01f079b5a23c77bc72a82968d19d74","tid":1450863,"uid":4335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:01:26.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=7015efb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=ab2e02fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"4687c329027225123f02b4b452a7aff4a38a34a2","tid":1450863,"uid":201095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:02:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警死全家<br />\n721 811"},{"pid":"203f8cf14367e7feef0dc9540871f7b55635db4f","tid":1450863,"uid":283109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:02:13.000Z","msg":"機場文宣整合post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450351</a><br />\n<br />\n「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場"},{"pid":"5621771a25f2a3ab554c6e7ea53ea265d6c6dd9f","tid":1450863,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":